des: "My 19-month-old son loves yogurt and squishy fruit but they're soooo messy. This way he can get both in a cool treat with no unnecessary sugar, and I can just hose him off afterward!"
ins: Blend yogurt, mango, pineapple chunks with juice, banana, and orange juice in a blender until smooth. Pour into ice pop molds; freeze until set, 4 to 6 hours.
